---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import GridBackground from '../../components/GridBackground.astro';
import ThemeToggle from '../../components/ThemeToggle.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Desarrollo web — Landings y sites que convierten | TOF" description="Construimos tu activo digital pensado para captar reuniones. Diseño + desarrollo + copy en un solo paquete. Performance, SEO y conversión.">

<GridBackground />

<nav id="navbar">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/web/" class="nav-logo">The Outbound <span>Force</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <a href="/web/">Inicio</a>
      <a href="/web/outbound">Outbound</a>
      <a href="/web/desarrollo-web" class="nav-active">Desarrollo Web</a>
      <a href="/web/faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="/web/contacto">Contacto</a>
      <ThemeToggle />
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/Jxg7er6LkiL6tGEw6" class="nav-cta magnetic-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Agendar Reunión</a>
    </div>
    <button aria-label="Menú" class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
  </div>
</nav>

<main id="main-content" tabindex="-1">
  <div style="height: 4.5rem;"></div>

  <section class="vp-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/web/" class="vp-back">← Volver al home</a>
      <span class="vp-kicker">Construimos tu web</span>
      <h1 class="vp-title">Landings y sites que <em>convierten visitas en reuniones</em>.</h1>
      <p class="vp-desc">No solo páginas que se ven bien — activos digitales pensados desde el día uno para capturar leads calificados. Diseño, desarrollo y copy en un solo paquete.</p>
      <div class="vp-actions">
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/Jxg7er6LkiL6tGEw6" class="btn btn-primary magnetic-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Pedir presupuesto</a>
        <a href="#que-hacemos" class="btn btn-ghost">Ver qué hacemos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="vp-section" id="que-hacemos">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Qué construimos</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Tu activo digital, completo.</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Cada proyecto incluye estos pilares — porque una landing sin copy o sin tracking no convierte.</p>

      <div class="vp-grid">
        <div class="vp-card reveal">
          <div class="vp-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Landing pages de conversión</h3>
          <p>Páginas optimizadas para captar leads de campañas de ads, outbound o orgánico. CTAs claros, prueba social y formularios que no fricciona.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card reveal">
          <div class="vp-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15 15 0 0 1 0 20M12 2a15 15 0 0 0 0 20"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Sitios corporativos B2B</h3>
          <p>Sites multi-página para empresas que necesitan presencia profesional: home, servicios, casos, blog y contacto. Performance y SEO de fábrica.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card reveal">
          <div class="vp-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M16 13H8M16 17H8M10 9H8"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Copywriting orientado a conversión</h3>
          <p>Cada palabra trabaja para mover al visitante hacia la acción. Investigación de audiencia, estructura AIDA y headlines que paran el scroll.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card reveal">
          <div class="vp-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M7 12l4-4 4 4 5-5"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Tracking y analítica</h3>
          <p>GA4, Meta Pixel, Hotjar y eventos custom configurados desde el inicio. Dashboards para que sepas qué fuente trae los leads que cierran.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card reveal">
          <div class="vp-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Performance y Core Web Vitals</h3>
          <p>Lighthouse 95+ en todos los ejes. Stack moderno (Astro), imágenes optimizadas, lazy-loading y CDN — todo para que cargue al instante.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vp-card reveal">
          <div class="vp-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg></div>
          <h3>SEO técnico y on-page</h3>
          <p>Schema markup, sitemaps, meta tags optimizados y arquitectura amigable para crawlers. Listo para rankear desde el día uno.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="vp-section vp-cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vp-cta-box reveal">
        <h2>¿Tenés un proyecto en mente?</h2>
        <p>Contanos qué necesitás y te respondemos con un presupuesto y plazo en menos de 48 horas. Sin compromiso.</p>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/Jxg7er6LkiL6tGEw6" class="btn btn-primary magnetic-btn" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Pedir presupuesto</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<Footer />

</Layout>

<style is:global>
/* ═══ Vertical detail page — light/dark adaptive ═══ */
footer { border-top: none !important; }

.vp-hero { padding: 3rem 0 4rem; }
.vp-back {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--textm);
  text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  transition: color 0.2s var(--ease);
}
.vp-back:hover { color: var(--accent); }
.vp-kicker {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--font-b);
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  color: var(--accent);
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
  padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem; border-radius: 999px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.vp-title {
  font-family: var(--font-d); font-weight: 800;
  font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  line-height: 1.05; color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  max-width: 820px;
}
.vp-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
.vp-desc {
  font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--text2); max-width: 640px;
  margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
}
.vp-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

.vp-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
.vp-section .section-desc { margin-bottom: 3rem; max-width: 560px; }

.vp-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.25rem;
}
.vp-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 1.75rem;
  transition: all 0.3s var(--ease);
}
.vp-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.35);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
}
.vp-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  background: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.08);
  border-radius: 12px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
}
.vp-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-d); font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}
.vp-card p {
  font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--text2);
}

/* CTA box stays dark-purple gradient in both modes (premium feel) */
.vp-cta-section { padding: 3rem 0 6rem; }
.vp-cta-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a1f3d 0%, #1a1625 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.25);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem;
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.12);
}
.vp-cta-box h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-d); font-weight: 800;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}
.vp-cta-box p {
  font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.55;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
}

/* ═══ Dark mode overrides ═══ */
body.dark .vp-back { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }
body.dark .vp-back:hover { color: #a78bfa; }
body.dark .vp-kicker {
  color: #a78bfa;
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.12);
}
body.dark .vp-title { color: #fff; }
body.dark .vp-title em { color: #a78bfa; }
body.dark .vp-desc { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); }
body.dark .vp-actions .btn-ghost {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04) !important;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85) !important;
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12) !important;
}
body.dark .vp-actions .btn-ghost:hover {
  border-color: #a78bfa !important;
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.1) !important;
  color: #fff !important;
}
body.dark .vp-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.15);
}
body.dark .vp-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.35);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
}
body.dark .vp-icon {
  background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.1);
  color: #a78bfa;
}
body.dark .vp-card h3 { color: #fff; }
body.dark .vp-card p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65); }

@media (max-width: 960px) { .vp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .vp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .vp-actions .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  .vp-cta-box { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
}
</style>

<script is:inline>
  var allR = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal,.reveal-left,.reveal-right,.reveal-scale");
  var rObs = new IntersectionObserver(function(e) {
    e.forEach(function(e) { e.isIntersecting && e.target.classList.add("active"); });
  }, { threshold: 0.08, rootMargin: "0px 0px -40px 0px" });
  allR.forEach(function(e) { rObs.observe(e); });

  window.addEventListener("scroll", function() {
    document.getElementById("navbar").classList.toggle("scrolled", window.scrollY > 50);
  });
  document.getElementById("menuToggle").addEventListener("click", function() {
    document.getElementById("navLinks").classList.toggle("open");
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('.magnetic-btn').forEach(function(btn) {
    var strength = 0.3;
    btn.addEventListener('mousemove', function(e) {
      var rect = btn.getBoundingClientRect();
      btn.style.transform = 'translate(' + (e.clientX - rect.left - rect.width / 2) * strength + 'px, ' + (e.clientY - rect.top - rect.height / 2) * strength + 'px)';
    });
    btn.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
      btn.style.transform = 'translate(0, 0)';
      btn.style.transition = 'transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)';
      setTimeout(function() { btn.style.transition = ''; }, 400);
    });
    btn.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() { btn.style.transition = 'none'; });
  });
</script>
